h3 Plane configuration
br
table.table
  thead.thead-dark
    tr
      th Class
      th No. of Columns
      th No. of Rows

  tbody
      tr
        td First Class
        td = @aeroplane.fc_column
        td = @aeroplane.fc_row
      tr
        td Business Class
        td = @aeroplane.bc_column
        td = @aeroplane.bc_row
      tr
        td Economy Class
        td = @aeroplane.ec_column
        td = @aeroplane.ec_row

h3 Trips 
br
table.table
  thead.thead-dark
    tr
      th Origin
      th Destination

  tbody
    - @aeroplane.trips.each do |trip|
      tr
        td = trip.origin
        td = trip.destination

